<P>
   MCCARTY-COLUMN _ DAYTON, Ohio _ As a community, our reaction to
the safe return of the Stewart family resembles that of parents of
errant teen-agers who came home too late from a party they weren't
allowed to attend in the first place. First, we want to hug them:
Thank God, you're home, safe and sound. Next, we want to scold
them: What on earth were you thinking, going off adventuring in a
marginally seaworthy ship? Taking your two children with you? Do
you have any idea how worried we were? (McCarty, Dayton Daily News)
MOVED
