<P>
   CELLULAR-TRANSCEPT (Manchester, N.H.) _ Transcept thinks it can
rid the landscape of cellular antenna towers with small
breadbox-sized transmitters that attach to utility poles. By Peter
Howe. 1170 words. PHOTO
