<SLUG> BC-SAM-E-MANIA-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SAM-E: IS IT THE E-Z WAY TO HEALTH AND HAPPINESS?
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JESSIE MILLIGAN 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
