<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS, attention features, technology page editors:
</P>
<P>
   Here is a list of selected computer-related stories of the past
week that we have repeated today, from  &UR; The N.Y. Times News
Service &LR;  and its parters, The Boston Globe, Cox News Service,
Bloomberg News, Hearst News Service, The Houston Chronicle, The
Arizona Republic, Kansas City Star, Fort Worth Star-Telegram, Los
Angeles Daily News, San Francisco Chronicle and Seattle
Post-Intelligencer.
</P>
<P>
   All these repeated stories carry a distinguishing ``CPT'' in the
slugline and move with an ``a'' general news category code.
</P>
<P>
   BC-CPT-RUSSIA-INTERNET-COX (Moscow) _ IN RUSSIA, BIG BROTHER
