<P>
   COX-HEALTH _ On Wednesday, Sept. 1, Cox Communications will
launch its new consumer health portal on 24 of Cox Interactive
Media's (CIMedia) city sites. A telephone briefing for the media
will be held Sep. 1 with the two primary content providers_
healthAtoZ.com and Cybear, Inc. (Katz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
