<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-01 19:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7731 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-HERBERT-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      09-01 0724
