   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   HANCOCK-PUBLIC (Boston) _ John Hancock's board, as expected, has
approved a plan to sell stock to management, policyholders, and
investors. Timetable calls for policyholders to approve deal Nov.
