<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-01 22:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7929 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-FOREIGN-BRIEFS-NYT &LR;      09-01 0945
